{"image_id": "PHM_2013_page_48", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "44", "bbox": [608.6, 1532.7, 629.4, 1555.8]}, {"text": "ITEM 7A.  QUANTITATIVE AND QUALITATIVE DISCLOSURES ABOUT MARKET RISK", "bbox": [85.5, 95.8, 931.9, 118.9]}, {"text": "We are subject to interest rate risk on our rate-sensitive financings to the extent long-term rates decline. The following", "bbox": [141.7, 145.9, 1131.9, 168.9]}, {"text": "tables set forth, as of December 31, 2013 and 2012, our rate-sensitive financing obligations, principal cash flows by scheduled", "bbox": [85.5, 170.9, 1144.1, 193.9]}, {"text": "maturity, weighted-average interest rates, and estimated fair value ($000’s omitted).", "bbox": [85.5, 195.9, 783.4, 218.9]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2013 for the", "bbox": [596.1, 237.2, 880.3, 260.2]}, {"text": "Years ending December 31,", "bbox": [616.9, 258.0, 861.2, 281.1]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [351.2, 308.0, 392.9, 331.1]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [453.3, 308.0, 495.0, 331.1]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [555.4, 308.0, 597.1, 331.1]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [657.6, 308.0, 699.2, 331.1]}, {"text": "2018", "bbox": [759.7, 308.0, 801.4, 331.1]}, {"text": "Thereafter", "bbox": [842.2, 308.0, 938.3, 331.1]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [977.6, 308.0, 1025.1, 331.1]}, {"text": "Fair", "bbox": [1084.6, 287.2, 1122.8, 310.3]}, {"text": "Value", "bbox": [1078.5, 308.0, 1130.6, 331.1]}, {"text": "Rate-sensitive liabilities:", "bbox": [89.6, 337.6, 285.0, 358.3]}, {"text": "Fixed interest rate debt:", "bbox": [102.1, 365.0, 284.0, 385.7]}, {"text": "Senior notes", "bbox": [127.1, 392.0, 220.4, 412.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [331.4, 393.9, 339.7, 412.4]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [388.3, 393.9, 405.0, 412.4]}, {"text": "$ 333,647", "bbox": [433.5, 393.9, 507.0, 412.4]}, {"text": "$ 465,245", "bbox": [535.6, 393.9, 609.1, 412.4]}, {"text": "$ 123,000", "bbox": [637.8, 393.9, 711.2, 412.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [739.9, 393.9, 748.2, 412.4]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [796.8,