 "$2,533,319", "bbox": [958.7, 610.7, 1034.3, 629.1]}, {"text": "$ 2,663,451", "bbox": [1062.9, 610.7, 1144.7, 629.1]}, {"text": "Average interest rate", "bbox": [127.1, 635.9, 283.4, 656.6]}, {"text": "—%", "bbox": [388.3, 637.7, 418.8, 656.2]}, {"text": "5.49%", "bbox": [477.8, 637.7, 521.0, 656.2]}, {"text": "5.24%", "bbox": [579.9, 637.7, 623.1, 656.2]}, {"text": "6.50%", "bbox": [682.0, 637.7, 725.2, 656.2]}, {"text": "7.63%", "bbox": [784.2, 637.7, 827.3, 656.2]}, {"text": "6.80%", "bbox": [901.0, 637.7, 944.1, 656.2]}, {"text": "6.36%", "bbox": [1005.1, 637.7, 1048.3, 656.2]}, {"text": "Derivative instruments and hedging activities", "bbox": [85.5, 691.9, 465.3, 714.9]}, {"text": "Pulte Mortgage is exposed to market risks from commitments to lend, movements in interest rates, and canceled or", "bbox": [141.7, 741.9, 1105.2, 764.9]}, {"text": "modified commitments to lend.  A commitment to lend at a specific interest rate (an interest rate lock commitment) is a", "bbox": [85.5, 766.9, 1083.6, 790.0]}, {"text": "derivative financial instrument (interest rate is locked to the borrower).  The interest rate risk continues through the loan closing", "bbox": [85.5, 791.9, 1156.4, 815.0]}, {"text": "and until the loan is sold to an investor.  We are generally not exposed to variability in cash flows of derivative instruments for", "bbox": [85.5, 816.9, 1144.4, 840.0]}, {"text": "more than approximately 75 days.  In periods of rising interest rates, the length of exposure will generally increase due to", "bbox": [85.5, 841.9, 1102.6, 865.0]}, {"text": "customers locking in an interest rate sooner as opposed to letting the interest rate float.", "bbox": [85.5, 866.9, 807.4, 890.0]}, {"text": "In order to reduce these risks, we use other derivative financial instruments, principally cash forward placement", "bbox": [141.7, 916.9, 1078.4, 940.0]}, {"text": "contracts on mortgage-backed securities and whole loan investor commitments, to economically hedge the interest rate lock", "bbox": [85.5, 941.9, 1123.5, 965.0]}, {"text": "commitment.  We enter into one of the aforementioned derivative financial instruments upon accepting interest rate lock", "bbox": [85.5, 966.9, 1093.1, 990.0]}, {"text": "commitments.  Changes in the fair value of interest rate lock commitments and the other derivative financial instruments are", "bbox": [85.5, 992.0, 1127.6, 1015.0]}, {"text": "recognized in Financial Services revenues.  We do not use any derivative financial instruments for trading purposes.", "bbox": [85.5, 1017.0, 1052.5, 1040.0]}, {"text": "Hypothetical changes in the fair values of our financial instruments arising from immediate parallel shifts in long-term", "bbox": [141.7, 1067.0, 1135.8, 1090.0]}, {"text": "mortgage rates of 50, 100, and 150 basis points would not be material to our financial results.", "bbox": [85.5, 1092.0, 864.2, 1115.1]}]}